title: FS: 29 different T201s all PSA graded 2-6; incl. several HOFers
author: scooter729

posts.post_title: FS: 29 different T201s all PSA graded 2-6; incl. several HOFers
posts.post_content:
Hey all – breaking up my T201s (29 of the 50 from the set) to fund a couple of purchases.  All PSA graded.  This is from a set I put together mostly 10-15 years ago, so these are older holders (hence no ½ grades – most of these were graded before they had the ½ grades).  I’m adding some scans and photos here, but can scan and send you any others you want to see better as well – just let me know….

Prices are net – prefer PayPal F/F, Venmo, etc.  but happy to figure out whatever payment works best for you.  Under $100, please add $5 shipping, more and the shipping is on me.  SOLD will trump any negotiations. 

Thanks for looking!
Scott
